OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death says he
OL,4,Cplanned to kill himself but 'lost
OL,5,Ccontrol'
OL,7,FA man who stabbed his wife to death as
OL,8,Fshe pushed their baby in a pram told a
OL,9,Fcourt he had intended to kill himself
OL,10,Fin front of her but "lost control"
OL,11,Fwhen he thought she was suggesting
OL,12,Fsomeone could replace him as a father
OL,13,Fto their son.
OL,15,FKulsuma Akter, 27, suffered more than
OL,16,F25 knife injuries in an attack by her
OL,17,Fhusband Habibur Masum, 26, after he
OL,18,Fconfronted her in a street in Bradford
OL,19,Fon April 6 last year.
