OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death says he
OL,4,Cplanned to kill himself but 'lost
OL,5,Ccontrol'
OL,7,FA trial has heard Masum tracked Ms
OL,8,FAkter to a refuge, where she had been
OL,9,Fstaying since January 2024 after he
OL,10,Fallegedly held a knife to her throat
OL,11,Ffollowing an assault at their home in
OL,12,FOldham in November 2023.
OL,14,FMasum, who found Ms Akter through her
OL,15,Fphone location, said he decided to go
OL,16,Fand see his wife and seven-month-old
OL,17,Fson the night before the fatal attack.
