OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death says he
OL,4,Cplanned to kill himself but 'lost
OL,5,Ccontrol'
OL,7,FGiving evidence through a Bengali
OL,8,Finterpreter, he told Bradford Crown
OL,9,FCourt: "On the night I was missing
OL,10,Fthem so dearly and I was really upset.
OL,11,FI thought that maybe if I killed
OL,12,Fmyself I won't hurt so much.
OL,14,F"Because I was really, really
OL,15,Fdepressed I kept changing my mind.
OL,16,FSometimes I thought that maybe if I
OL,17,Fwent away very far I would be able to
OL,18,Fforget her and forget my son."
