OL,7,FHe said he was "still optimistic" he
OL,8,Fcould save the marriage and told
OL,9,Fjurors his plan was "to explain to her
OL,10,Fhow I'm feeling, that I don't want to
OL,11,Fbe separated from my family".
OL,13,F"Then I thought that even if after all
OL,14,Fthat she still doesn't understand I
OL,15,Fwill just kill myself in front of
OL,16,Fher," Masum said.
