OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death says he
OL,4,Cplanned to kill himself but 'lost
OL,5,Ccontrol'
OL,7,FAsked how he ended up using the knife
OL,8,Fto attack Ms Akter instead, he said:
OL,9,F"I lost my control. I tried to talk to
OL,10,Fher, I tried to explain to her about
OL,11,Fseeing my son.
OL,13,F"I was trying to make her consider
OL,14,Fabout our child and that he needs a
OL,15,Ffather.
OL,17,F"She said 'you don't need to worry
OL,18,Fabout our son, there's no lacking of a
OL,19,Ffather for him'."
