OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death says he
OL,4,Cplanned to kill himself but 'lost
OL,5,Ccontrol'
OL,7,FHe told the court: "There was a lot
OL,8,Fgoing through my head including maybe
OL,9,Fsomebody else was going to be
OL,10,Freplacing my role, my position ... as
OL,11,Ffather."
OL,13,FMasum broke down in tears as he said:
OL,14,F"I totally lost control", later saying
OL,15,Fthat the next thing he could remember
OL,16,Fwas walking along the road with
OL,17,Fbloodstains on his hand.
OL,19,FAsked if he remembered what he did
OL,20,Fwith the knife, he said: "No."
