OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death says he
OL,4,Cplanned to kill himself but 'lost
OL,5,Ccontrol'
OL,7,FMasum denied assaulting Ms Akter or
OL,8,Fthreatening to kill her during the
OL,9,Fincident in November 2023.
OL,11,FHe accused her of making false claims
OL,12,Fof domestic violence as a way to stay
OL,13,Fin the UK, saying he wanted to return
OL,14,Fto Bangladesh once his visa expired,
OL,15,Fand she did not.
OL,17,FThe court heard he told police at the
OL,18,Ftime: "She knows if you suspect your
OL,19,Fhusband the law will take you and keep
OL,20,Fyou safe so you won't have to go back
OL,21,Fhome."
