OL,7,FAsked about this, Masum told the
OL,8,Ftrial: "I tried to explain to them
OL,9,Fthat she was trying to make false
OL,10,Fallegations against me to create a
OL,11,Fdomestic violence case to appeal to
OL,12,Fstay in the UK."
OL,14,FHe repeated the claim he made to
OL,15,Fpolice that he believed Ms Akter had
OL,16,Fcaused the bruising on her face
OL,17,Fherself.
OL,19,FMasum denies murdering Ms Akter but
OL,20,Fhas pleaded guilty to manslaughter and
OL,21,Fpossession of a knife.
